scene.message:
Maki's Mom: Maki, dear...{nl}
It's your mother!!{nl}
Let's go home together!{waitkey}{clearbox}Look, everyone was worried{nl}
and came all this way{nl}
just for you!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Don't come!!{nl}
Everyone... why did you come?!{waitkey}{nl}
You know what kind of{nl}
girl I am, don't you?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Sonomura...{nl}
Maybe it's too much to ask{nl}
you not to mind it, but...{waitkey}{clearbox}Everybody envies others{nl}
now and then, right?{nl}
I do too.{waitkey}{clearbox}And besides, you were used.{nl}
Kandori's the bad guy, right?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: How many times did I{nl}
try to kill you all?!{nl}
Why are you so kind?!{waitkey}{clearbox}Stop pitying me.{nl}
Being pitied only{nl}
makes it worse...{waitkey}Someone like me should{nl}
just die!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Don't be so spoiled!!{nl}
You reap what{nl}
you sow!!{waitkey}{clearbox}If you want to die so badly,{nl}
why haven't you?{nl}
Don't scream of things{nl}
you can't even do!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Pity? Don't make me{nl}
laugh. They all came here{nl}
of their own will because{nl}
they understand you.{waitkey}{clearbox}Besides, do you think{nl}
you live all alone?{waitkey}{clearbox}Every person is kept alive{nl}
by those around them.{nl}
That's why we each bear{nl}
responsibility.{waitkey}{clearbox}Your easy way out would{nl}
leave a wound in many{nl}
hearts that never heals.{waitkey}{clearbox}If you still want to die,{nl}
do as you please. Forget{nl}
it all if you wish.{waitkey}But we won't forget you,{nl}
who were our friend.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Now, let's go back.{nl}
We'll save Sonomura{nl}
ourselves.{waitkey}Giving up halfway isn't{nl}
my style.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Wait!!{wait_fr:88}{nl}
I'm sorry, everyone...{nl}
Me... take me with you too.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Heh...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Of course we will.{nl}
Welcome back, Sonomura!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mom: Uu...{nl}
Thank you, everyone...{nl}
Thank you...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Mama...{nl}
I'm sorry...{nl}
I was a bad girl...{waitkey}{clearbox}I remember everything now.{nl}
I always longed to see you,{nl}
lonely and hurting alone...{waitkey}{clearbox}I forgot you worked{nl}
for my sake, resented you...{nl}
I'm so sorry...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mom: It's all right...{nl}
it's all right now.{nl}
I'm sorry, Maki, dear...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: I'm sorry,{nl}
Nanjo, {ctl07:1}...{nl}
Truly, thank you...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...{wait_fr:88}My apologies.{nl}
I was a bit harsh{nl}
with my words.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Nanjo...{nl}
Are you embarrassed?!{nl}
Oh, I get it!{waitkey}{clearbox}You've never been{nl}
thanked by anyone before,{nl}
'cause you're such a sourpuss.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Q-quiet, Inaba!{nl}
Honestly...{nl}
Now then, {ctl0f:1}, let's go back!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: {ctl0f:1} is right.{nl}
You reap what{nl}
you sow!!{waitkey}{clearbox}If you want to die so badly,{nl}
why haven't you?{nl}
Don't scream of things{nl}
you can't even do!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: I've come to my senses.{nl}
Even if I'm only a dream,{nl}
a phantom, a shadow,{nl}
I'm still me, after all...{waitkey}{clearbox}And besides, I have all of{nl}
you - {ctl07:1} and everyone...{nl}
Nothing's more reassuring.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Well, I guess{nl}
Nanjo's hair-splitting{nl}
comes in handy now and then.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hmph.{nl}
Being thanked by people{nl}
is an everyday affair.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: ...We can't stand{nl}
around feeling warm and{nl}
fuzzy forever.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: I'm so glad...{nl}
But {ctl07:1},{nl}
if I ever became like that...{waitkey}{clearbox}Sorry, that was a{nl}
strange thing to say.{wait_fr:88}{nl}
You'd surely save me, right?{nl}
If it were you...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: I'm so glad...{nl}
But {ctl07:1},{nl}
if I ever became like that...{waitkey}{clearbox}Sorry, that was a{nl}
strange thing to say.{wait_fr:88}{nl}
You would surely save me,{nl}
wouldn't you? If it's you...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: {ctl0f:1} said such{nl}
harsh things, Ayase{nl}
didn't know what'd happen.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: {ctl08:12033} said such{nl}
harsh things, Ayase{nl}
didn't know what'd happen.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mom: I don't know how{nl}
to thank you all...{waitkey}{clearbox}Maki is a lucky girl,{nl}
surrounded by such warm{nl}
friends... Truly, thank you...{waitkey}{ret}
